
在每个主机上面创建一个 /linux_c/c_language 文件夹

---
 - hosts: all
   tasks:
     - name: Create a directory named c_language in every host
       shell: mkdir -p /linux_c/c_language


在每个主机的c_language 文件夹里创建一个allen2024.sh 文件

---
 - hosts: all
   tasks:
     - name: Create a directory named allen2024.sh in every host
       shell: touch /linux_c/c_language/allen2024.sh
